        "translations": {
          "en": "He said: Abu Hafs Umar ibn Muhammad al-Sayrafi reported to me from Muhammad ibn Hammam al-Iskafi, who reported from Ahmad ibn Idris, who reported from Ahmad ibn Muhammad ibn Isa al-Ash'ari, from Ali ibn al-Nu'man, from Fudayl ibn Uthman, from Muhammad ibn Shurayh, who said: I heard Abu Abdillah Ja'far ibn Muhammad, peace be upon them both, say:",
